  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 24a04ab43ec46244e881a610d2970b30, type: 3}
  m_Name: Kael_Quest_2
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestInfo
  initialDialog:
  - Your new sword looks sharp, but your gear needs an upgrade if you want to survive
    the deeper woods.
  - I can craft a protective charm for you, but the materials are not easy to get.
    First, I need a Bear Heart. You can usually find a bear roaming near the northern
    hills.
  - The tricky part will be the 2 Green Gems. They are exclusively found inside Slimes,
    and those gelatinous pests only emerge after the sun goes down.
  - 'Fair warning: the drop rate for those gems is quite low. You will likely have
    to hunt down several Slimes in the dark before you find what you need. Stay vigilant.'
  initialDialogClips:
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 7017c56b79d8fa942b2213ea0916bf72, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 1de51cbe19d78f347abd8c719cd998fa, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 1b63c1ef8a0be5b408c278435f851b2e, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: fd1f83dbd5c44cb4587cf62fefc27d49, type: 3}
  acceptOption: I will get you the Bear Heart and the Green Gems. See you soon.
  acceptAnswer: Good hunting! Don't forget to bring a torch, the wilderness gets
    pitch black at night.
  acceptAnswerClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: fa422c79d18fe214e898aca985ef5fbd, type: 3}
  declineOption: Hunting in the dark sounds too dangerous right now. I need more
    preparation.
  declineAnswer: A wise decision if you're not ready. The night claims many careless
    adventurers. Come back when you feel braver.
  declineAnswerClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 1003907fb91915e4fae0326f87261f21, type: 3}
  comebackAfterDecline: Ready to face the night and hunt down those beasts?
  comebackAfterDeclineClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 7a8e25a4d10e78c4e8f90d3b70c1c7a7, type: 3}
  comebackInProgress: You are still missing some materials. Remember, I need 1 Bear
    Heart and 2 Green Gems. Wait until nightfall to hunt the Slimes, and keep trying
    if they don't drop the gems right away!
  comebackInProgressClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: f4ee3642d66feab41aa60c795e7b50f8, type: 3}
  comebackCompleted: You made it back in one piece! And you brought exactly what
    I asked for. That was no easy task.
  comebackCompletedClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 890707d51db55674cb4efbfc1547c442, type: 3}
  finalWords: Take this reward, as promised. You are quickly proving yourself to
    be a true survivor.
  finalWordsClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: f06745903e7a431428d0d97c8b70521b, type: 3}
  coinReward: 100
  rewardItem1: MRE
  rewardItem2: 
